void ShowPOVMatrix(byte ca[][46][3],int Width){
   for(int row = 0;row<Width;row++){
    for(int column = 0;column<46;column++){
         byte currentH =  ca[row][column][0];
          byte currentS =   ca[row][column][1];
          byte currentV = ca[row][column][2];
          leds[(45-column)].setHSV(currentH,currentS,currentV);
          leds[91-(45-column)].setHSV(currentH,currentS,currentV);
          leds[(45-column)+92].setHSV(currentH,currentS,currentV);
      }
      FastLED.show();
      delay(currentDelay);
   }
}
void Cylon(){
  // First slide the led in one direction
  for(int i = 0; i < 46; i++) {
    // Set the i'th led to red 
    leds[i] = CRGB::Red;
                leds[91-i]= CRGB::Red;
                leds[i+92]= CRGB::Red;
                // Show the leds
    FastLED.show();
    // now that we've shown the leds, reset the i'th led to black
    leds[i] = CRGB::Blue;
                leds[91-i]= CRGB::Blue;
                leds[i+92]= CRGB::Blue;
                // Wait a little bit before we loop around and do it again
    delay(currentDelay);
  }

  // Now go in the other direction.  
  for(int i = 46-1; i >= 0; i--) {
    // Set the i'th led to red 
    leds[i] = CRGB::Red;
                leds[91-i]= CRGB::Red;

    FastLED.show();
    // now that we've shown the leds, reset the i'th led to black
    leds[i] = CRGB::Blue;
                leds[91-i]= CRGB::Blue;
                leds[i+92]= CRGB::Blue;
    // Wait a little bit before we loop around and do it again
    delay(currentDelay);
  }  
}
void CheckSerial(){
    int AvailBytes = Serial2.available();
    String newDelay="";
    String newBrightness = ""; 
    String newMode = "";
    char buffer[64]; 
    int index = 0;
    if (AvailBytes>0)
    {
      char command = Serial2.read();
      bool othercommands = false;
      while(Serial2.available()&&!othercommands){
        char current = Serial2.read();
        if(current=='|'&&Serial2.available()){
          othercommands=true;
        }
        if(!othercommands){
          buffer[index] = current;
          index++;
        }
      }  
      switch(command){
        case 'D':
          newDelay = buffer;
          currentDelay = newDelay.toInt();
          break;
        case 'I':
          newDelay = buffer;
          intermission = newDelay.toInt();
          break;          
        case 'B':
          newBrightness = buffer;
          currentBrightness = newBrightness.toInt();
          FastLED.setBrightness(currentBrightness);   
          break;  
          case 'M':
            newMode = buffer;
            currentMode= newMode.toInt();
          break;        
      }
      if(othercommands){
        CheckSerial();
      }
    }
}
void pollingDelay(int delaytime){
  int incrDelay = 15;
  if(delaytime<15){
    incrDelay = delaytime;
  }
  while(1==1){
    CheckSerial();
    delay(incrDelay);
    
    delaytime -= incrDelay;
    if(delaytime<=0){
      return;
    }  
  }
}
